title: Puppy_Linux_Tahr64
description:
tahrpup64 beta 

(size 224M)

 this is tahrpup64 beta 6.0.3.8 build with 64bit ubuntu 14.04 trusty tahr libs. 

 jwm, palemoon, vlc-2.2.1, mtpaint, abiword, geany, hexchat, gnumeric, qpdf viewer ,urxvt ,simple screen recorder, dunst(OSD),getflash, getjava, Mydbox ,ListDD ,pupsysinfo, mp-5, deadbeef, sticky-JWM, samba, pburn, gnugcc (gcc switcher) and lots more. 

 testing....: init that allows to load upto 30.sfs files 'ASRI', 
 'giros' fsck for ext4 & giros updated partview.
